@BaseUrl = http://localhost:5133
@AuthToken = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Đăng nhập (Lấy Token)
POST {{BaseUrl}}/api/Auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employeeCode": "ADMIN001",
  "password": "Password123!",
  "rememberMe": true
}

### 2. Đổi mật khẩu (Yêu cầu Token)
POST {{BaseUrl}}/api/Auth/change-password
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "Password123!",
  "newPassword": "NewPassword@2025",
  "confirmPassword": "NewPassword@2025"
}

### 3. Lấy danh sách nhân viên (Yêu cầu Token)
# Ví dụ: PagedResult với Filter và Search
POST {{BaseUrl}}/api/Employees/get-employees
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pagination": {
    "pageIndex": 1,
    "pageSize": 10,
    "search": "Khai Toan",
    "orderBy": ["fullName asc"],
    "filters": {
      "status": "Active"
    }
  }
}

### 4. Logout (Thu hồi Refresh Token)
POST {{BaseUrl}}/api/Auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE"
}
